Package app.Models

Class QueryResult

java.lang.Object
app.Models.QueryResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.QueryResultI, Serializable
public class QueryResult extends Object implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.QueryResultI
Represents the results of a query within a sensor network. This class can manage both gathered sensor data and boolean-based results indicating the presence or absence of certain conditions at sensor nodes.
